  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Pain is defined as a sensorial and emotional phenomenon and lead consequences on the
      cognition. These consequences could be increased with usual treatment. So the aim of this
      study is to explore these cognitive consequences.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Pilot prospective study with parallel groups
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
